headline: PSEG Long Island to Continue Serving Long Island and the Rockaways for the Next Five Years
summary: The Long Island Power Authority Board of Trustees has awarded PSEG Long Island an extension on the existing contract to continue to operate the electric grid on Long Island and in the Rockaways for the next five years.
